# Workflow Communication Layer (Phase 2, v0.2 seo-health-v2 milestone)
# Shared bearer token between ops-api and the seo-health-v2 terminal workflow.
# Generate with: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
# Rotation: update in Railway env (ai-calling-backend) AND seo-health-v2 terminal .env,
# then redeploy both. NEVER commit the actual value. Minimum 32 chars.
WORKFLOW_API_TOKEN=
